- display the database and order it by item.
SELECT * FROM clothingstore ORDER BY item;

- what is the sum of the prices for the entire store?
SELECT SUM(price) FROM clothingstore;

- what is the avergae price of all the clothing items in the store?
SELECT AVG(price) FROM clothingstore; 
